(1, 'Home', 'block', '', '', '', 'HOME_TOP', 'Active', '<h1 style="margin: 0 0 0.8125em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 190%;">Subscribe to any newsletter of the world without giving your email address away anymore!</h1>\n<p><strong> <span style="font-size: large;">It''s like your own dog trained to bring your newsletters when you need them, to the place you want them&nbsp;...</span> </strong></p>', '<h1 style="margin: 0 0 0.8125em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 190%;">Abonniere alle Newsletter der Welt ohne deine E-Mail-Adresse mehr herauszugeben!</h1>\n<p><strong> <span style="font-size: large;">Es ist wie dein eigener Hund, der so dressiert ist, dir deine Newsletter zu bringen, wenn du sie brauchst, dahin, wo du sie haben m&ouml;chtest&nbsp;...</span> </strong></p>', '<h1 style="margin: 0 0 0.8125em; font-weight: bold; font-size: 190%;">Inscris-toi pour toutes les lettres d&rsquo;information du monde sans plus besoin d&rsquo;indiquer ton adresse e-mail&nbsp;!</h1>\n<p><strong> <span style="font-size: large;">C&rsquo;est comme ton chien dress&eacute; &agrave; t&rsquo;apporter tes newsletters quand t&rsquo;en as besoin, l&agrave; o&ugrave; tu le veux&nbsp;...</span> </strong></p>', '', ''),
(2, 'Home', 'block', '', '', '', 'HOME_IMAGE', 'Active', '<p><img src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home.PNG" border="0" alt="" /></p>', '<p><img src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home_german.png" border="0" alt="" /></p>', '<p><img src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home_french.png" border="0" alt="" /></p>', '', ''),
(3, 'Home', 'block', '', '', '', 'HOME_SIGN_UP_BOTTOM', 'Active', '<p><span class="freeaccount_text">And from now on knewdog! will protect your mailbox from spam and virus.</span></p>\n<p><span class="freeaccount_text"><a style="color: gray;" title="Learn more ..." href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/#learnmore">Learn more ...</a> </span></p>', '<p><span class="freeaccount_text">Und von jetzt an wird knewdog! dein Postfach vor Spam und Virus sch&uuml;tzen.</span></p>\n<p><span class="freeaccount_text"><a style="color: gray;" title="Erfahre mehr ..." href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/#learnmore">Erfahre mehr ...</a> </span></p>', '<p><span class="freeaccount_text">Et &agrave; partir de maintenant knewdog! va prot&eacute;ger ta boite contre le spam et les virus.</span></p>\n<p><span class="freeaccount_text"><a style="color: gray;" title="En savoir plus ..." href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/#learnmore">En savoir plus ...</a> </span></p>', '', ''),
(4, 'Sign up', 'block', '', '', '', 'SIGNUP_HEAD', 'Active', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">You want to get newsletters without giving your email address away anymore?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Sign up now. <u>It&#39;s FREE !</u></div>\n', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">Du m&ouml;chtest Newsletter bekommen, ohne deine E-Mail-Adresse mehr herausgeben zu m&uuml;ssen?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Registriere dich jetzt.&nbsp;<u>Es ist KOSTENLOS !</u></div>\n', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">Tu veux recevoir des lettres d&rsquo;information sans plus besoin d&rsquo;indiquer ton adresse e-mail ?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Inscris-toi toute suite.&nbsp;<u>C&#39;est GRATUIT !</u></div>\n', '', ''),
(5, 'Sign up', 'block', '', '', '', 'SIGNUP_HOW_DOES', 'Active', '<section id="howdoesitwork">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle howdoesitwork_title">\n<h2>How does it work?</h2>\n</div>\n<div class="dash_jwl_one_fourth">\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Sign up with your e-mail or your preferred social account. It&rsquo;s free!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Browse our extensive newsletter library online!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Read the newsletters you like online.</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth last"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Did not find your favourite newsletter? We will order it for you.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="clearboth">&nbsp;</div>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5em;">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style="color: #e46c0a; font-size: 16px;">Our promise:<br />No newsletter provider will ever get access to your e-mail address!</span></h3>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>\n<section id="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle newfeaturestobecomingup_title">\n<h2>New features to be coming up!</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<li>Get all your favourite newsletters in one single e-mail.</li>\n<li>Choose date and time when you want to get your newsletters.</li>\n<li>Select individual e-mail address for different newsletter topics (e.g. work e-mail address for work related topics).</li>\n<li>The feedbacks of other users will help you find the best newsletter for your needs.</li>\n<li>Quick and easy newsletter subscription on any site you are surfing on.</li>\n<li>Company accounts optimise the information flow for every employee through effective newsletter management.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>', '<section id="howdoesitwork">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle howdoesitwork_title">\n<h2>Wie funktioniert es?</h2>\n</div>\n<div class="dash_jwl_one_fourth">\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Registriere dich mit deiner E-Mail oder deinem bevorzugten Social Account. Es ist kostenlos!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Durchst&ouml;bere unsere umfangreiche Newsletter-Bibliothek online!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Lies die Newsletter, die du magst, online.</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth last"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Du kannst deine Lieblings-Newsletter nicht finden? Wir bestellen sie f&uuml;r dich.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="clearboth">&nbsp;</div>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5em;">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style="color: #e46c0a; font-size: 16px;">Wir versprechen:<br />Kein Newsletter-Anbieter wird jemals Zugang zu deiner E-Mail-Adresse erhalten!</span></h3>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>\n<section id="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle newfeaturestobecomingup_title">\n<h2>Neue Funktionen kommen bald!</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<li>Erhalte alle deine Lieblings-Newsletters in einer einzigen E-Mail.</li>\n<li>W&auml;hle Datum und Uhrzeit, wann du deine Newsletter bekommen m&ouml;chtest.</li>\n<li>W&auml;hle individuellle E-Mail-Adressen f&uuml;r verschiedene Newsletter-Themen aus (z.B. berufliche E-Mail-Adresse f&uuml;r Berufsbezogene Themen).</li>\n<li>Die Feedbacks der anderen Nutzer werden dir helfen, die besten Newsletter f&uuml;r deine Bed&uuml;rfnisse zu finden.</li>\n<li>Schnelle und einfache Newsletter-Bestellung auf jeder Webseite, die du besuchst.</li>\n<li>Company Accounts optimieren den Informationsfluss f&uuml;r jeden Mitarbeiter durch effektives Newsletter-Management.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>', '<section id="howdoesitwork">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle howdoesitwork_title">\n<h2>Comment &ccedil;a marche&nbsp;?</h2>\n</div>\n<div class="dash_jwl_one_fourth">\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Enregistres-toi avec ton e-mail ou ton compte social pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;. C&rsquo;est gratuit&nbsp;!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Fouilles notre vaste biblioth&egrave;que de lettres d&rsquo;information en-ligne&nbsp;!</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Lis les newsletters que tu aimes en-ligne.</div>\n<div class="jwl_one_fourth last"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-257" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" alt="" width="113" height="113" /> Tu ne peux pas trouver ton newsletter pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;&nbsp;? Nous allons le commander pour toi.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="clearboth">&nbsp;</div>\n<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5em;">&nbsp;</p>\n<h3><span style="color: #e46c0a; font-size: 16px;">Notre promesse :<br />Aucun &eacute;diteur de newsletter n&rsquo;aura jamais acc&egrave;s &agrave; ton adresse e-mail&nbsp;!</span></h3>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>\n<section id="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<article>\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle newfeaturestobecomingup_title">\n<h2>Nouvelles fonctionnalit&eacute;s bient&ocirc;t disponibles&nbsp;!</h2>\n</div>\n<ul class="newfeaturestobecomingup">\n<li>Re&ccedil;ois tous tes newsletters favoris&eacute;s en un seul e-mail.</li>\n<li>Choisis la date et l&rsquo;heure quand tu veux recevoir tes newsletters.</li>\n<li>Choisis des adresses e-mail individuelles pour chaque sujet de newsletter (par ex. l&rsquo;adresse e-mail du bureau pour toutes les informations en relation avec ton travail).</li>\n<li>Les feedbacks des autres utilisateurs t&rsquo;aideront &agrave; trouver les meilleurs newsletters pour tes besoins.</li>\n<li>Abonnement rapide et facile de newsletters sur toutes les sites web que tu visites.</li>\n<li>Company accounts optimiseront le flux d&rsquo;information de chaque employ&eacute; gr&acirc;ce &agrave; notre management de newsletters effectif.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr /></article>\n</section>', '', ''),
(6, 'Sign up', 'block', '', '', '', 'SIGNUP_BOT', 'Active', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">You want to get newsletters without giving your email address away anymore?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Sign up now. <u>It&#39;s FREE !</u></div>\n', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">Du m&ouml;chtest Newsletter bekommen, ohne deine E-Mail-Adresse mehr herausgeben zu m&uuml;ssen?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Registriere dich jetzt. <u>Es ist KOSTENLOS !</u></div>\n', '<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 190%; line-height: normal;">Tu veux recevoir des lettres d&rsquo;information sans plus besoin d&rsquo;indiquer ton adresse e-mail ?</div>\n\n<div class="signupfree_blacktitle" style="font-size: 18px;">Inscris-toi toute suite. <u>C&#39;est GRATUIT !</u></div>\n', '', ''),
(7, 'Help', 'help_page', 'Help', 'Hilfe', 'Aide', 'HELP_PAGE', 'Active', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>We&#39;re here to help!</h2>\n</div>\n\n<p>Explore the help topics, and if you can&#39;t find your answer or just want to say &#39;hi&#39;, please <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><strong>email us</strong></a>. <strong>We would appreciate a short feedback from you as well.</strong></p>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>What would you like help with?</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/gettingstarted/"><strong>Getting started</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/"><strong>Questions and answers (FAQ)</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contactus"><strong>Contact us</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Find us on the Interwebs</h3>\n\n<p>We&lsquo;re always happy to keep you updated on<br />\n<a href="http://www.twitter.com/knewdog_news"><strong>Twitter</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.facebook.com/knewdog"><strong>Facebook</strong></a>, <a href="http://plus.google.com/+Knewdog"><strong>Google+</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/knewdog-"><strong>Linkedin</strong></a> and <a href="https://www.xing.com/companies/knewdog%2521"><strong>Xing</strong></a> too.<br />\nJust come by our pages and say &sbquo;hi&lsquo;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Wir sind f&uuml;r dich da!</h2>\n</div>\n\n<p>Schau dir alle Hilfe-Themen an, und wenn du nicht die richtige Antwort findest oder du einfach &ldquo;Hallo&rdquo; sagen m&ouml;chtest, bitte sende uns eine&nbsp;<a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><strong>E-Mail</strong></a>. <strong>Au&szlig;erdem w&uuml;rden wir uns sehr &uuml;ber ein kurzes Feedback von dir freuen.</strong></p>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Wobei k&ouml;nnen wir dir helfen?</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/gettingstarted/"><strong>Einstieg</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/"><strong>Fragen und Antworten (FAQ)</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contactus"><strong>Kontaktiere uns</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Finde uns im Interweb</h3>\n\n<p>Wir freuen uns immer, dich auf den aktuellen Stand zu bringen mit unseren Seiten auf&nbsp;<br />\n<a href="http://www.twitter.com/knewdog_news"><strong>Twitter</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.facebook.com/knewdog"><strong>Facebook</strong></a>, <a href="http://plus.google.com/+Knewdog"><strong>Google+</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/knewdog-"><strong>Linkedin</strong></a> und <a href="https://www.xing.com/companies/knewdog%2521"><strong>Xing</strong></a>.<br />\nKomm einfach vorbei und sag&rsquo; &ldquo;Hallo&rdquo;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Nous sommes l&agrave; pour t&rsquo;aider&nbsp;!</h2>\n</div>\n\n<p>Explores les pages de notre Help-Center, et si tu ne peux pas trouver la bonne r&eacute;ponse ou si tu veux juste dire &ldquo;bonjour&rdquo;, envoies nous un&nbsp;<a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><strong>e-mail</strong></a>. <strong>Nous appr&eacute;cierons un court feedback de ta part &eacute;galement.</strong></p>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Comment pouvons nous t&rsquo;aider&nbsp;?</h3>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/gettingstarted/"><strong>Pour bien commencer</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/"><strong>Foire aux Questions (FAQ)</strong></a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contactus"><strong>Contactes nous</strong></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h3>Rejoins nous sur l&rsquo;Interweb</h3>\n\n<p>Nous serions heureux de te tenir au courant sur &nbsp;<br />\n<a href="http://www.twitter.com/knewdog_news"><strong>Twitter</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.facebook.com/knewdog"><strong>Facebook</strong></a>, <a href="http://plus.google.com/+Knewdog"><strong>Google+</strong></a>, <a href="http://www.linkedin.com/company/knewdog-"><strong>Linkedin</strong></a> et <a href="https://www.xing.com/companies/knewdog%2521"><strong>Xing</strong></a> &eacute;galement.<br />\nJuste viens nous voir sur nos pages et dis &ldquo;bonjour&rdquo;.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '', ''),
(8, 'Help', 'help_page', 'Getting Started', 'Einstieg', 'Pour bien commencer', 'gettingstarted', 'Active', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Getting Started</h2>\n\n<p>Welcome! This guide is intended as a brief introduction to using knewdog!. For more information, please see the <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/" style="color: gray;" title="Help-Centre"><strong>Help pages</strong></a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Introduction to knewdog!</h3>\n\n<p>With knewdog!, you can manage your newsletters in any web browser. Once you <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/" style="color: gray;" title="Sign up!"><strong>sign up</strong></a> for a free account, you can <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/wp-login.php" style="color: gray;" title="Login"><strong>login</strong></a> to the member area to get started.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>Guide is coming soon !</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Einstieg</h2>\n\n<p>Willkommen! Dieser Guide dient als kurze Einf&uuml;hrung zur Nutzung von knewdog!. F&uuml;r mehr Information besuche bitte die <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/" style="color: gray;" title="Help-Centre"><strong>H<strong>i</strong>lfe Seiten</strong></a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Einf&uuml;hrung zu knewdog!</h3>\n\n<p>Mit knewdog! kannst du deine Newsletter in jedem Webbrowsler managen. Einmal f&uuml;r einen kostenlosen Account <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/" style="color: gray;" title="Sign up!"><strong>registriert</strong></a>, kannst du dich in den Mitgliederbereich <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/wp-login.php" style="color: gray;" title="Login"><strong>einloggen</strong></a> starten.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>Guide kommt bald !</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Pour bien commencer</h2>\n\n<p>Bienvenue ! Ce guide est destin&eacute; &agrave; une courte introduction pour l&#39;usage de knewdog!. Pour plus d&#39;information, viens voir nos <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/" style="color: gray;" title="Help-Centre"><strong>Pages Aide</strong></a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h1>Introduction &agrave; knewdog!</h1>\n\n<p>Avec knewdog!, tu peux manager tes newsletters dans chaque navigateur web. Une fois <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/" style="color: gray;" title="Sign up!"><strong>enregistr&eacute;</strong></a> pour un compte gratuit, tu peux te <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/wp-login.php" style="color: gray;" title="Login"><strong>connecter</strong></a> &agrave; l&#39;espace membre et commencer.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>Guide sera bient&ocirc;t disponible !</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '', ''),
(9, 'Help', 'help_page', 'FAQ', 'FAQ', 'FAQ', 'faq', 'Active', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Questions and answers (FAQ)</h2>\n\n<p>Explore the Questions and answers, and if you can&rsquo;t find your answer or just want to say &lsquo;hi&rsquo;, please <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact/" style="color: gray;" title="Contact us!">email us</a>.</p>\n\n<h3>Accounts</h3>\n\n<ul style="margin-left:30px">\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowDoISignUp" style="color: gray;">How do I sign up?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#WhatWillYouDoWithMyEmailAddress" style="color: gray;">What will you do with my email address?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowMuchDoesItCost" style="color: gray;">How much does it cost to sign up?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowDoILogin" style="color: gray;">How do I login to my account?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowCanIUpgradeToPro" style="color: gray;">How can I upgrade to Premium?</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h3>Features</h3>\n\n<ul style="margin-left:30px">\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#WhatKindOfNewsletters" style="color: gray;">What kind of newsletters are in your database?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#DoINeedToLoginToRead" style="color: gray;">Do I need to login to read newsletters?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#IsItPossibleToDownload" style="color: gray;">Is it possible to download a newsletter?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#DontFindMyNewsletter" style="color: gray;">What can I do if I don&#39;t find my favourite newsletter in your database?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#CanIgiveFeedback" style="color: gray;">Can I give feedback to a newsletter?</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h3>General</h3>\n\n<ul style="margin-left:30px">\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowCanIHelpYou" style="color: gray;">How can I help you developing the knewdog! project?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#HowCanIPromote" style="color: gray;">I have a newsletter. How can I promote it on knewdog?</a></li>\n	<li><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/help/faq/#WhoIsBehind" style="color: gray;">Who&rsquo;s behind knewdog?</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style="clear: both;">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<hr />\n<p><strong><a name="HowDoISignUp"></a>How do I sign up?</strong><br />\nYou can sign up directly on the home page or go to the <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/" style="color: gray;" title="Sign up!">sign up page</a>. Fill up the form with a username of your choice and a valid personal email address. Confirm. That&#39;s it.<br />\nTo save time, you can sign up using your existing Facebook or Google account. Just click on the logo and confirm.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="WhatWillYouDoWithMyEmailAddress"></a>What will you do with my email address?</strong><br />\nNothing. We need your email address for our administration processes only. We promise, no newsletter provider will ever get access to your e-mail address and it will never be rented, traded or sold!</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="HowMuchDoesItCost"></a>How much does it cost to sign up?</strong><br />\nNothing. The sign up is free.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="HowDoILogin"></a>How do I login to my account?</strong><br />\nClick on <em>Login to My knewdog!</em> on the right of the menu, enter your username and email address.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="HowCanIUpgradeToPro"></a>How can I upgrade to Premium?</strong><br />\nGo to your profile on &quot;My knewdog!&quot;. Here, you&#39;ll find a link &quot;<a href="https://www.knewdog.com/premium-account" style="color: gray;" title="Upgrade to Premium!">Upgrade to Premium</a>&quot;.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="WhatKindOfNewsletters"></a>What kind of newsletters are in your database?</strong><br />\nAll kind. You will find business related topics as well as leisure related ones. The only topics you won&#39;t find are those with content that is unlawful, misleading, malicious or discriminatory. The following content is banned from our website: hate speech, threat, pornographic; inciting violence; containing nudity or graphic or gratuitous violence.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="DoINeedToLoginToRead"></a>Do I need to login to read newsletters?</strong><br />\nYes. Our extensive newsletter database is for our members only. Please <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup/" style="color: gray;" title="Sign up!">sign up</a> for a free account to get access to our newsletter database.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="IsItPossibleToDownload"></a>Is it possible to download a newsletter?</strong><br />\nYes. Once you are logged in, you can download all newsletters.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="DontFindMyNewsletter"></a>What can I do if I don&#39;t find my favourite newsletter in your database?</strong><br />\nDon&#39;t worry. Just send us an email with the link to the website where you want to get the newsletter from. We will order it for you. Don&#39;t sign up by yourself on that site. We will inform you as soon as your newsletter will be available on our website. The final version of knewdog! will provide a plugin that allows you to quick and easy order newsletters on any site you are surfing on directly.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="CanIgiveFeedback"></a>Can I give feedback to a newsletter?</strong><br />\nYes. Go to &quot;My knewdog&quot; and open the tab &quot;My newsletters&quot;. Here you can rate each of your newsletters.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="HowCanIHelpYou"></a>How can I help you developing the knewdog! project?</strong><br />\nWe are looking for freelance team members and for sponsors as well. If you are interested, contact us by using the <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contactus" style="color: gray;" title="Contact us!">contact form</a>.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="HowCanIPromote"></a>I have a newsletter. How can I promote it on knewdog?</strong><br />\nThe Prelaunch version offers you a free, fast and easy way to publish your newsletters. Just send us your newsletter by using our <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contactus" style="color: gray;" title="Contact us!">contact form</a>. We will check your content and get in touch with you for further processing. The final version of knewdog! will provide tools for newsletter providers to promote your newsletters and to reach numerousness readers with one click.</p>\n\n<p><strong><a name="WhoIsBehind"></a>Who&rsquo;s behind knewdog?</strong><br />\nknewdog! is founded and developed by Ines Sachs, expert for business development and entrepreneur. In her daily business she always used newsletters to keep her know-how up-to-date. And there always was the challenge to manage all these information. She knew she couldn&rsquo;t be the only one having this problem and finding a solution could help millions of newsletter readers. That&rsquo;s why the idea of knewdog! came up. Visit Ines&rsquo; personal blog at <a href="http://www.cactus-competence.com" style="color: gray;" target="_blank" title="CACTUS COMPETENCE">CACTUS COMPETENCE</a> to lean more.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Fragen und Antworten (FAQ)</h2>\n<strong>Bitte entschuldige, diese Seite ist noch nicht ins Deutsche &uuml;bersetzt. Um die Inhalte anzuzeigen, klicke bitte auf die britische Fahne.</strong></div>\n</div>\n', '<div class="help_leftbar_inner">\n<div class="page_helptitle">\n<h2>Foire aux Questions (FAQ)</h2>\n<strong>Pardon, cette page n&rsquo;est pas encore traduite en Fran&ccedil;ais. Pour afficher le contenu, cliquer sur le drapeau anglais.</strong></div>\n</div>\n', '', ''),
(10, 'About', 'page', 'What for?', '', '', 'about', 'Active', '<section class="homepage" id="container">\n<div class="about_main">\n<article class="about_left">\n<h2 class="about_tit">What it does for you&hellip;</h2>\n\n<p class="pabout">We make newsletters easy to manage.</p>\n\n<h3 class="about_tit3">Did you ever get fed up with all these e-mail newsletters and info mails jamming your in-box?</h3>\n\n<ul class="cope">\n	<li>How to cope with all these informations?</li>\n	<li>How to filter the crucial ones out <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_1">of the</span> spam?</li>\n	<li>How to get rid of the spam?</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class="pabout">We found <strong>the answer</strong> to these questions and that&rsquo;s why we are developing <strong>knewdog! The World&rsquo;s <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_8">Safest</span> newsletter Library.</strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout">You want to get newsletters without giving your email address away anymore?</p>\n\n<h3 class="sign"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup">Sign up</a></strong></h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">right now for a free account!</p>\n\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h3>\n</article>\n\n<article class="about_right">\n<div style="margin-top: 25px; margin-left: 20px;">\n<p class="pabout"><strong><span style="color: #808080; margin-top: 20px; font-size: medium;"><em>You want to promote your newsletter?</em></span></strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080; font-size: small;"><em>The final version of knewdog! will provide tools for newsletter providers to promote your newsletters and to <strong>reach numerousness readers with one click</strong>.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><em>The current version offers you a <strong>free, fast and easy way to publish your newsletters</strong>. Just send us your newsletter by using our </em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><span style="color: #808080; text-decoration: underline;">contact form</span></a></strong></span><em>. We will check your content and get in touch with you for further processing.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><strong>Don&rsquo;t miss that instrument for your <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_6">newsletter publishing</span>!</strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>What you get&hellip;</h3>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p><img alt="What you get from knewdog!" border="0" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-253" height="433" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home.png" width="411" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul class="quick">\n	<li><strong>Quick and easy newsletter management with only one account to&hellip;</strong>\n\n	<ul class="quick1">\n		<li><strong>read</strong> all your favourite newsletters <strong>online</strong></li>\n		<li><strong>decide when and where</strong> you want to read newsletters</li>\n		<li><strong>choose</strong> newsletters <strong>according to your topic</strong> from our extensive database and <strong>browse</strong> our wide <strong>newsletter archive</strong></li>\n		<li>read <strong>feedbacks</strong> from other users to find the best newsletter for your needs</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong>Maximum <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_2">privacy protection</span> with&hellip;</strong>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<ul>\n			<li><strong>No need</strong> to spread your private e-mail address in sign up forms to get informations any more. We&rsquo;ll do that for you, using our own e-mail address!</li>\n			<li><strong>100% spam and <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_3">virus protection</span></strong> as all newsletter provider is checked by knewdog!</li>\n			<li><strong>No</strong> newsletter provider will ever get <strong>access to your e-mail address!</strong></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>More features coming soon!</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>How does it work ?</h3>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" width="180" /> Sign up with your e-mail or your preferred social account. It&rsquo;s free!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" width="180" /> Browse our extensive newsletter <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_7">database online</span>!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" width="180" /> Read the newsletters you like online.</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" width="180" /> Did not find your favourite newsletter? We will order it for you.</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Need help?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">Have a question? Then please visit our <a href="#">Help-Centre</a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Like the idea?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">We are looking for freelance team members and for sponsors as well. If you are interested, contact us by using the <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact/">contact form</a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Who&rsquo;s behind?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">knewdog! is founded and developed by Ines Sachs, expert for <span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_4">business development</span> and entrepreneur. In her daily business she always used newsletters to keep her know-how up-to-date. And there always was the challenge to manage all these information. She knew she couldn&rsquo;t be the only one having this problem and finding a solution could help millions of newsletter readers. That&rsquo;s why the idea of knewdog! came up.</p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Our company is called <a href="http://cactus-competence.com/">CACTUS COMPETENCE</a> and besides consulting, it provides business development as well. One of these exciting business ideas we are currently working on is knewdog!</p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Read our <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/blog/">Blog</a> to learn more about knewdog!</p>\n</section>\n', '<section class="homepage" id="container">\n<div class="about_main">\n<article class="about_left">\n<h2>Wof&uuml;r ist es gut&hellip;</h2>\n\n<p class="pabout">Wir machen es einfach, Newsletter zu managen.</p>\n\n<h3>Warst du auch schon mal genervt von den vielen E-Mail-Newslettern und Info-Mails, die deinen Posteingang verstopfen?</h3>\n\n<ul class="cope">\n	<li>Wie soll man mit diesen vielen Informationen zurecht kommen?</li>\n	<li>Wie soll man die wirklichen wichtigen aus dem Spam herausfiltern?</li>\n	<li>Wie wird man Spam los?</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class="pabout">Wir haben<strong> die Antwort</strong> auf diese Fragen gefunden und darum entwickeln wir<strong> knewdog! Die Weltweit Sicherste Newsletter-Bibliothek.</strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Du m&ouml;chtest Newsletter bekommen, ohne deine E-Mail-Adresse herausgeben zu m&uuml;ssen?</p>\n\n<h3 class="sign"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup">Registriere dich</a></strong></h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">gleich jetzt f&uuml;r einen kostenlosen Account!</p>\n\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h3>\n</article>\n\n<article class="about_right">\n<div style="margin-top: 25px; margin-left: 20px;">\n<p class="pabout"><strong><span style="color: #808080; margin-top: 20px; font-size: medium;"><em>M&ouml;chtest du deinen Newsletter bewerben?</em></span></strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080; font-size: small;"><em>Die Endversion von knewdog! wird Tools f&uuml;r Newsletter-Anbieter haben, um ihre Newsletter zu bewerben und <strong>zahllose Leser mit einem Klick zu erreichen</strong>.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><em>Diese aktuelle Version bietet dir einen <strong>kostenlosen, schnellen und einfachen Weg, deine Newsletter zu ver&ouml;ffentlichen</strong>.&nbsp;Sende uns einfach deinen Newsletter mit unserem </em><em><span style="color: #808080;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><span style="color: #808080; text-decoration: underline;">Kontakt-Formular</span></a></strong></span><em>. </em></span>Wir werden ihn inhaltlich pr&uuml;fen und dich zum weiteren Ablauf kontaktieren.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><strong><span class="q74zk5z" id="q74zk5z_6">Nutze dieses Instrument f&uuml;r dein Newsletter Publishing</span>!</strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Was du bekommst&hellip;</h3>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p><img alt="Was du bekommst von knewdog!" border="0" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-253" height="433" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home_german.png" width="411" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul class="quick">\n	<li><strong>Schnelles und einfaches Newsletter-Management mit nur einem Account f&uuml;r&hellip;</strong>\n\n	<ul class="quick1">\n		<li><strong>Lies</strong> alle deine Lieblings-<strong>Newsletter online</strong></li>\n		<li><strong>Entscheide, wann und wo</strong> du Newsletter lesen m&ouml;chtest</li>\n		<li><strong>W&auml;hle</strong> Newsletters zu deinem<strong> Thema</strong> aus unserer gro&szlig;en Datenbank und<strong> durchst&ouml;bere</strong> unser umfangreiches Newsletter<strong> Archiv</strong></li>\n		<li>Lies <strong>Feedbacks</strong> von anderen Nutzern, um die besten Newsletter f&uuml;r deine Bed&uuml;rfnisse zu finden</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong>Maximaler Schutz der Privatsph&auml;re mit&hellip;</strong>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<ul>\n			<li><strong>Nie wieder</strong> deine private E-Mail-Adresse in Einschreibe-Formulare eintragen, um Informationen zu erhalten. Wir machen das f&uuml;r dich und nutzen dabei unsere eigene E-Mail-Adresse!</li>\n			<li><strong>100% Spam und Virus gesch&uuml;tzt</strong>, denn jeder Newsletter-Anbieter wird von knewdog! gepr&uuml;ft.</li>\n			<li><strong>Kein</strong> Newsletter-Anbieter wird jemals<strong> Zugang zu deiner E-Mail-Adresse</strong> erhalten!</li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Mehr Funktionen kommen bald!</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Wie funktioniert es?</h3>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" width="180" /> Registriere dich mit deiner E-Mail oder deinem bevorzugten Social Account. Es ist kostenlos!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" width="180" /> Durchst&ouml;bere unsere umfangreiche Newsletter-Bibliothek online!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" width="180" /> Lies die Newsletter, die du magst, online.</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" width="180" /> Du kannst deine Lieblings-Newsletter nicht finden? Wir bestellen sie f&uuml;r dich.</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Brauchst du Hilfe?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">Hast du eine Frage? Bitte besuche unser&nbsp;<a href="#">Help-Centre</a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Gef&auml;llt dir diese Idee?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">Wir suchen freiberufliche Team-Mitglieder und auch Geldgeber. Wenn du Interesse hast, kontaktiere uns &uuml;ber unser <a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact/">Kontakt-Formular</a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Wer steckt dahinter?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">knewdog! wurde von Ines Sachs gegr&uuml;ndet und entwickelt. Sie ist Expertin f&uuml;r Business Development und Entrepreneur. F&uuml;r ihre t&auml;gliche Arbeit nutzt sie schon immer Newsletter, um ihr Know-How auf dem neuesten Stand zu halten. Und da war schon immer die Herausforderung, all diese Informationen zu managen. Sie wusste, sie konnte wohl kaum die einzige sein, die dieses Problem hat, und dass eine L&ouml;sung daf&uuml;r Millionen von Newsletter-Lesern helfen w&uuml;rde. So entstand die Idee f&uuml;r knewdog!</p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Unser Unternehmen hei&szlig;t <a href="http://cactus-competence.com/">CACTUS COMPETENCE</a> und bietet neben Beratung auch die Entwicklung von Gesch&auml;ftsideen an. Eine dieser spannenden Ideen, an der wir zur Zeit besonders intensiv arbeiten, ist knewdog!</p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Lies unseren&nbsp;<a href="https://www.knewdog.com/blog/">Blog</a> um mehr &uuml;ber knewdog! zu erfahren!</p>\n</section>\n', '<section class="homepage" id="container">\n<div class="about_main">\n<article class="about_left">\n<h2>Ce qu&rsquo;il fait pour toi&hellip;</h2>\n\n<p class="pabout">Nous faisons les newsletters faciles &agrave; manager.</p>\n\n<h3>T&rsquo;en avais d&eacute;j&agrave; marre de tous ces newsletters et infos par e-mail qui remplissent ta boite&nbsp;?</h3>\n\n<ul class="cope">\n	<li>Comment g&eacute;rer toutes ces informations&nbsp;?</li>\n	<li>Comment filtrer les infos importantes de tout ce spam&nbsp;?</li>\n	<li>Comment se d&eacute;barrasser du spam&nbsp;?</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class="pabout">Nous avons trouv&eacute;&nbsp;<strong>la r&eacute;ponse</strong>&nbsp;&agrave; ces questions et c&rsquo;est pourquoi nous d&eacute;veloppons <strong>knewdog! La Biblioth&egrave;que de Lettres d&#39;Information la Plus Fiable du Monde.</strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout">Tu veux recevoir des lettres d&rsquo;information sans plus besoin d&rsquo;indiquer ton adresse e-mail&nbsp;?</p>\n\n<h3 class="sign"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/signup">Engrestres-toi</a></strong></h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">toute suite pour un account gratuit&nbsp;!</p>\n\n<h3 style="text-align: left;">&nbsp;</h3>\n</article>\n\n<article class="about_right">\n<div style="margin-top: 25px; margin-left: 20px;">\n<p class="pabout"><strong><span style="color: #808080; margin-top: 20px; font-size: medium;"><em>Tu veux faire de la pub pour ton newsletter&nbsp;?</em></span></strong></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080; font-size: small;"><em>La version finale de knewdog! va offrir des outils aux auteurs de lettres d&rsquo;information pour faire de la publicit&eacute; pour leurs newsletters et pour <strong>cibler innombrable lecteurs avec un seul clic</strong>.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><em>La version actuelle vous offre un moyen <strong>gratuit, rapide et facile pour publier votre lettres d&rsquo;information</strong>.&nbsp;Il suffit de nous envoyer votre lettre d&rsquo;information en utilisant notre </em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><a href="https://www.knewdog.com/contact"><span style="color: #808080; text-decoration: underline;">formulaire de contact</span></a></strong></span><em>. Nous allons v&eacute;rifier le contenu de votre newsletter et vous recontacter pour les marches &agrave; suivre.</em></span></p>\n\n<p class="pabout"><span style="color: #808080;"><strong>Ne ratez pas cet instrument pour la publication de votre newsletter&nbsp;!</strong></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Ce que tu auras&hellip;</h3>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half">\n<p><img alt="Ce que tu auras de knewdog!" border="0" class="alignleft size-full wp-image-253" height="433" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/formimg_home_french.png" width="411" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class="jwl_one_half last">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul class="quick">\n	<li><strong>Management de newsletters rapide et facile avec un seul compte pour&hellip;</strong>\n\n	<ul class="quick1">\n		<li><strong>lire</strong> tous tes lettre d&rsquo;information pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;es<strong> en ligne</strong></li>\n		<li><strong>d&eacute;cider quant et o&ugrave;</strong> tu veux lire tes newsletters</li>\n		<li><strong>choisir</strong> des newsletters de notre large base de donn&eacute;s<strong> selon ton sujet</strong> et<strong> fouiller</strong> notre vaste newsletter<strong> archive</strong></li>\n		<li>lire les <strong>feedbacks</strong> des autres utilisateurs pour trouver les meilleurs newsletters pour tes besoins</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><strong>Maximum de protection de donn&eacute;s personnels avec&hellip;</strong>\n	<ul>\n		<li>\n		<ul>\n			<li><strong>Plus besoin</strong> de diffuser ton adresse e-mail priv&eacute; dans les formulaires d&rsquo;inscription pour obtenir des informations. Nous allons faire &ccedil;a pour toi en utilisant notre propre adresse e-mail&nbsp;!</li>\n			<li><strong>100% spam et virus protection</strong> comme tout &eacute;diteur de newsletters sera v&eacute;rifi&eacute; par knewdog!</li>\n			<li><strong>Aucun</strong> &eacute;diteur de newsletter n&rsquo;aura jamais<strong> acc&egrave;s &agrave; ton adresse e-mail&nbsp;!</strong></li>\n		</ul>\n		</li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li>Plus de fonctionnalit&eacute;s seront bient&ocirc;t disponibles&nbsp;!</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Comment &ccedil;a marche&nbsp;?</h3>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram1.png" width="180" /> Enregistres-toi avec ton e-mail ou ton compte social pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;. C&rsquo;est gratuit&nbsp;!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram2.png" width="180" /> Fouilles notre vaste biblioth&egrave;que de lettres d&rsquo;information en-ligne&nbsp;!</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram3.png" width="180" /> Lis les newsletters que tu aimes en-ligne.</div>\n\n<div class="work_im"><img border="0" height="180" src="https://www.knewdog.com/assets/img/pictogram4.png" width="180" /> Tu ne peux pas trouver ton newsletter pr&eacute;f&eacute;r&eacute;&nbsp;? Nous allons le commander pour toi.</div>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>Besoin d&rsquo;aide&nbsp;?</h3>\n\n<p class="pabout">Tu as une question&nbsp;? Viens voir notre&nbsp;<a href="#">Help-Centre</a>.</p>\n\n<hr />\n<h3>L