helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">in sales by listening\r\nto one of the greatest</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">marketing minds\r\never..Dan Kennedy.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">He is THE master of the\r\npsychology of selling. He</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">understands the\r\nunconscious &ldquo;mental triggers&rdquo; you</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">have to set off to\r\nmake a reluctant prospect</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">suddenly eager to pull\r\nout a credit card.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">He&rsquo;s made a\r\nscience of not only refusing to take</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">&ldquo;No&rdquo; for\r\nan answer &ndash; but uncovering the secrets of</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">making someone happily\r\nsay &ldquo;Yes&rdquo; instead.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">I''ve personally paid\r\nDan thousands of dollars to</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">get this kind of\r\ninformation...and it was worth</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">every penny.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Now, you can learn from\r\nthe master marketer</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">himself for\r\nfree.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Dan''s created a new\r\nvideo series called the </font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">&quot;7 Secrets of\r\nWriting Mind Control Copy&rdquo;.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3"><a href="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/13055/7992fafa0fb66887/384786015/f3261494d1722a2c"><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">You''d be crazy not to watch this</font></a>...it''s million</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">dollar info.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">He''s even giving you\r\nthe blueprint exposing the</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">seven &quot;dark&quot;\r\ncopy techniques that really push</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">people''s emotional\r\nbuttons.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">This opportunity\r\ndoesn&rsquo;t come along often. Dan</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">doesn&rsquo;t just\r\nstep out and share a lifetime of</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">secrets on a regular\r\nbasis.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">So, take a few minutes\r\nand <a href="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/13057/aa0ff7ce021f4811/384786015/f3261494d1722a2c"><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">listen to what he has</font><br /><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">to say.</font></a> I guarantee\r\nyou&rsquo;ll be blown away.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">To higher\r\nprofits,</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Rich</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">P.S. - Remember, there\r\nare reasons people don&rsquo;t</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">want to buy &ndash;\r\