(255, 'AUG1478619N', 'AUG1478619N140808063559', 'child', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', 0, 'NO', 'Brian Tracy', 'Make your prospects'' buying decision STUPID easy...', 'Brian Tracy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Brian Tracy', 'NO', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">\r\n<html>\r\n	<head>\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us">\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n	<title>A Message From Brian Tracy</title>\r\n	</head>\r\n	<body><div style=''height:2px;''><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/images/btis182874277.gif" width="10" height="2" alt=""></div>\r\n		<style type="text/css">\r\n	p {margin-bottom: 1em;}\r\n\r\n			.NLTitle {font-weight: normal; font-size: 16pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial;}\r\n			.NLSubtitle {font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: none;}\r\n			.NLAuthor {font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic;}\r\n		</style>\r\n		\r\n		<span style="color: #222222; font-weight:normal; font-size:12pt; font-family: Arial;">\r\n\r\n		<p>aug1478619n,</p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.5em;">Many years ago I created a program called the Psychology of Selling.</span></p>\r\n<p>To date, it is my most popular, best selling program of all time, because no matter what profession or industry you&rsquo;re in&hellip;you&rsquo;re selling something&mdash;whether it&rsquo;s an idea, product or service, or yourself.</p>\r\n<p>And the only way to sell well is to first understand the reasons WHY people buy--the fascinating psychological triggers that influence people to make buying decisions.</p>\r\n<p>As Dan Kennedy always says, &ldquo;It&rsquo;s not what&rsquo;s in the box.&rdquo; It&rsquo;s how "what&rsquo;s in the box" is perceived by the customer.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s hard to argue with that, right?&nbsp; People look everywhere they can for reasons NOT to buy &ndash; because they&rsquo;d rather keep their money than give it to you. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>That&rsquo;s why we all need the brilliance of marketing legend Dan Kennedy.&nbsp; He&rsquo;s made a science of not only refusing to take &ldquo;No&rdquo; for an answer &ndash; but uncovering the secrets of making them happily say &ldquo;Yes&rdquo; instead.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>He understands the unconscious &ldquo;mental triggers&rdquo; you have to set off to make a reluctant prospect suddenly eager to buy from you.</p>\r\n<p>This is the kind of information that sales managers, business owners, and experts have paid me tens of thousands of dollars to teach them.</p>\r\n<p>In a brand-new video, Dan Kennedy reveals some of the "mental triggers" that have helped my clients to personally double--or even triple--their sales numbers. No joke.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206284&amp;ebr=182874277">Learn the 7 mind control secrets that make people buy. </a></p>\r\n<p>Dan doesn''t give this kind of valuable information away for free very often, so I highly recommend you take advantage of it now. The psychology behind selling is really amazing.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206285&amp;ebr=182874277">Watch the video here, absolutely free</a>.</p>\r\n<p>To your success,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n\r\n		</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>Get Involved!</strong><br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/twitter.gif" alt="twitter" title="Twitter" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nFollow me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206286&amp;ebr=182874277" style="color:#1d3c5a">Twitter</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/facebook.gif" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nBecome a fan on\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206287&amp;ebr=182874277" style="color:#1d3c5a">Facebook</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/linkedin.gif" alt="LinkedIn" title="LinkedIn" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nConnect with me on \r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206288&amp;ebr=182874277" style="color:#1d3c5a">LinkedIn</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/youtube.gif" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nWatch me on <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206289&amp;ebr=182874277" style="color:#1d3c5a">Youtube</a>.<br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/blog.gif" alt="Blog" title="Blog" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; Check out my <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206290&amp;ebr=182874277" style="color:#1d3c5a">Blog</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n		<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><br /><br /><a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="https://www.knewdog.com"> <b style="color:#e46c0a;">To manage your subscriptions, visit your profile at www.knewdog.com.</b></a> <a style="color: #1d3c5a;" href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=206291&amp;ebr=182874277">Privacy Policy</a> &copy; 2000-2014, Brian Tracy International. All Rights Reserved.</p>\r\n\r\n	</body>\r\n</html>', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', '', 0, '2014-08-08 06:35:59', '2014-08-08 06:35:59', 'Active'),
