<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="header" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="title" style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="text" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Happy Birthday celebrations are in order&nbsp;Knewdog&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12854/5e7234997c20ffb3/2512952/839b6a7f1501e2a1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"><img align="left" alt="The Suitcase Entrepreneur Book" border="0" height="212" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-9e202030-97c4-4f65-808b-7bf9d268209b-v2" style="padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal" title="The Suitcase Entrepreneur Book" width="138" hspace="10" vspace="10" /></a>Can you believe it&rsquo;s been exactly one year since I self-published my book <a href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/book" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">The Suitcase Entrepreneur? </a>Cos I certainly can&rsquo;t. How time flies.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Yet I remember it so vividly. I was in Vancouver, Canada filled with excitement but verging on burnout from handling all the moving parts of not only writing my book, but launching and marketing it and continuing my book tour.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">S</span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">o you can imagine how ecstatic I was when just a few days after it was released on Amazon it moved up the ranks to become a No #1 bestseller in not one, but three categories!</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"></span><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">There&rsquo;s no better feeling than your friends, family and freedom fighting community supporting you and your wildest dreams - to write a book that could change lives - like these people reading it now.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12848/bdfbe7c4ccbe14c0/2512952/839b6a7f1501e2a1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"><img align="bottom" alt="Create freedom in business and adventure" border="0" height="436" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-8c99e9d6-7095-4168-b033-c8dc5226f6f8-v2" style="margin: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;" title="Create freedom in business and adventure" width="545" /></a> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<strong></strong></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">To celebrate I''ve finally made it available to buy through me if you&rsquo;re not able to get an Amazon account or want to use PayPal not credit card. </span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12850/f10a695c9e1103f2/2512952/839b6a7f1501e2a1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">If you buy through my book website</a>&nbsp;you also get two chapters of the audio book as a bonus. And YES the full audio book is coming too. Available this month on my site and Audible!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Either way I&rsquo;d love it if you could please spread the news with friends you think would benefit from my book&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Click to tweet:</strong> &nbsp;<a href="http://ctt.ec/mUPHa" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Create freedom in business and adventure in life with the Suitcase Entrepreneur book!. #buynow</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Now, since my book is all about traveling the world and building your business, it&rsquo;s entirely fitting that in this week&rsquo;s video I answer a community member&rsquo;s question about what the first steps to take are to start building your online business.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12846/3a11ae8a0c865bc8/2512952/839b6a7f1501e2a1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"><img align="bottom" alt="The First 4 Steps to Starting an Online Business" border="0" height="363" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-73ef6c5e-115c-477f-9e3d-575e3ffbe36f-v2" style="margin: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;" title="The First 4 Steps to Starting an Online Business" width="538" /></a> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I know that figuring out what to do first can be the hardest part, which is why I am walking you through 4 key steps to starting your online business (and you&rsquo;ll get 3 more in next week&rsquo;s video).</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n We&rsquo;ll cover everything from determining your ideal customer to finding your sweet spot, so if you want to create a business and life you love, <a href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/lifestyle-business-videos/starting-an-online-business/" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">this video is for you</a>!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n If I do say so myself, this a pretty damn good video. And to add to that this week&rsquo;s podcast is pretty awesome and high energy too thanks to my guests, Jill and Josh Stanton. </span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n On this week&rsquo;s podcast they tell you all about what it&rsquo;s been like to give up their roots, travel around Southeast Asia, all the while building their 5-figure a month affiliate marketing business as a couple. </span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n If you want high energy, laughter, fun and some serious biz and relationship tips be sure to <a href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/103" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">listen to this podcast now</a>!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Here&rsquo;s to choosing freedom always!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Natalie xx</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong>Natalie Sisson</strong></font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Chief Adventurer And Freedom Fighter</font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><a href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com" target="_blank">suitcaseentrepreneur.com</a><br /> natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com&nbsp;<br /> </font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="footer" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 20px; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255);" valign="top">\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 10px; font-family: verdana; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\n<div contentid="paragraph" style="font-size: 10px; font-family: verdana; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\n<div>\r\nIf you no longer wish to receive this lovely weekly Highflyer from me then I''ll be sad to see you: \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<a href="https://www.knewdog.com" shape="rect" style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(6,69,173);"><b style="color:#e46c0a;">To manage your subscriptions, visit your profile at www.knewdog.com.</b></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 10px; font-family: verdana; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\nNatalie Sisson<br>NE 7th Ave<br>Portland, Oregon 97211<br>United States\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n