adding-bottom:0px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div id="bt1" style="color:#ffffff;padding-top:17px;font-size:16px;">Brian Tracy''s</div>\r\n<div id="bt2" style="color:#ffffff;line-height:100%;margin-top:7px;font-weight:bold;font-size:25px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Success Newsletter</div>\r\n<div id="bt3" style="color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:15px;padding-top:7px;font-size:14px;">For Business and Financial Achievement</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding-left:20px;vertical-align:bottom;">\r\n<div id="bt4" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;width:1px;height:1px;display:none;"><img id="btimg" src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/email/brian-tracy.png" alt="" height="1" width="1" style="width:1px;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr></table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="line" style="background-color:#c2c2c2;height:2px;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--[if gte mso 9]>*/</style><![endif]-->\r\n<div id="top-nav" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;">\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132316&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132317&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132318&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132319&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132320&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132321&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div id="main" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:16px;">\r\n<p>Hi aug1499926n,</p>\r\n<p>First off, I wanted to make sure you claimed your free special report the other day.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Remember, it''s called "The Way to Wealth&rdquo; and it&rsquo;s designed to give you all the information you need to earn more money on your energy invested &ndash; resulting in a more satisfying, more enjoyable life.</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132322&amp;ebr=183490307">You can still claim your copy here.</a></p>\r\n<p>Now, let me ask you this, how would you like to get out of debt?</p>\r\n<p>Even better, how would you like to live with the confidence that you&rsquo;re building a financial fortress; that when you retire, you&rsquo;ll be a millionaire?</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132323&amp;ebr=183490307">Now you can.</a></p>\r\n<p>Thanks to my powerful new program, the &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple&rdquo; series, you have the opportunity to develop the mindset and skills to not only get out of debt, but to also become wealthy.<br /><br />This set comprises my NEWEST wealth-building program, with two of my most powerful wealth enhancing training tools-<strong>-at an INCREDIBLE discount!</strong><br /><br /> <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132324&amp;ebr=183490307">Order my "Wealth Building Made Simple" series here</a>--new promo pricing!</p>\r\n<p>It includes:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Wealth Building Made Simple (a 15-CD set + Mp3''s)</li>\r\n<li>Strategic Advancement Digital DVD (a 2-hour training video)</li>\r\n<li>The Way to Wealth Digital Workbook (a 250-page workbook to customize your journey)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132325&amp;ebr=183490307"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/wealth/assets/img/program_all.png" alt="" width="261" /></a></p>\r\n<p>During this program, you learn to start with nothing and become wealthy: to escape debt with a fool-proof system, to transform your thinking about yourself and money, to develop the million-dollar habits you need, and to get rich in your own special way.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132326&amp;ebr=183490307">Get the details here, and get special promo pricing!</a></p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re like so many of my students, I can guess the thoughts that may be going through your mind right now:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>I don&rsquo;t have ANYTHING. Forget a financial fortress &ndash; I can barely pay my monthly electric bill.</li>\r\n<li>I&rsquo;m not smart enough to make my mortgage, much less millions.</li>\r\n<li>I just have bad luck. I&rsquo;d never be lucky enough to become wealthy.</li>\r\n<li>Something always comes up that keeps me from saving money &ndash; I&rsquo;ll never be able to save.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132327&amp;ebr=183490307">Good news: you&rsquo;re completely wrong.</a></p>\r\n<p>No matter where you are now, you have inside of you the potential and the ability to get out of debt, and to build a healthy financial future for yourself.</p>\r\n<p>And I''ll teach you how, in the &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple&rdquo; series.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132328&amp;ebr=183490307">Get it now.</a></p>\r\n<p>You hold the power to create your own wealth. And you&rsquo;ll do so faster and easier by following in the footsteps of those who have done it before you.</p>\r\n<p>The lessons in the &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple Series&rdquo; are based not only on my own experience, but also on years of research into what makes success.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132329&amp;ebr=183490307">Order it today!</a></p>\r\n<p>To your financial freedom,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. I''m offering the &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple Set&rdquo; at an incredibly low price &ndash; just like my other "Made Simple" programs, this WILL sell out.&nbsp;<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132330&amp;ebr=183490307">If you&rsquo;re interested, order your copy now.</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132331&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132332&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132333&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132334&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132335&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=132336&amp;ebr=183490307" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div> \r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>\r\n<td id="footer" style="color:#222222;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;background-color:#d9d9d9;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:14px;">\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Change Your Email</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;"><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/ce.