(233, 'AUG1483403N', 'AUG1483403N140805040201', 'child', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', 0, 'NO', 'Natalie Sisson', 'The first step to creating a profitable online business', 'Natalie Sisson', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Natalie Sisson', 'NO', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head><body>\r\n<div id="mainContent" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: rgb(255,255,255); width: 100%; height: 100%;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="preheader" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 10px 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div contentid="preheader" style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div>\r\nHaving trouble viewing this email? <a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11886/6bb32f58f345d429/2484668/6ac82dc418d16534" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Click here</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="header" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255);">\r\n<div>\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div style="display: block; text-align: center;">\r\n<img align="bottom" alt="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" border="0" height="82" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-e5ba5c06-5717-4bff-a538-3704df735fa9-v2" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; vertical-align: bottom;" title="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" width="600" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="header" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="title" style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="text" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Hey Knewdog&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> When you signed up to my newsletter, I promised to also share with you the 6 Steps to Building a profitable business you love and a lifestyle of freedom.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> It&rsquo;s taken me almost four years of being in business to hone and refine these steps for myself, and I&rsquo;ve helped hundreds of clients and customers to apply them too.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> So you can rest assured that these steps do really work and they&rsquo;ve gotten people real and tangible results.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Today I&rsquo;d like to jump straight into&hellip;&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Step 1: Implement Your Vision + 1 Page Profit Plan&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Having a clear vision for your life and business is quite possibly the most powerful and critical step to take that will literally transform your business, mindset and lifestyle overnight.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Why then don&rsquo;t more people take the time to actually map out what they&rsquo;d love their life to look like, and where their business will be in 3 years time?</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Because it takes some effort and time to sit down and let your imagination wander to what you&rsquo;d really love your life to look like. It also takes guts to dream big and then put it out there publicly. </span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">However if you really, truly want to build a business you love and your dream lifestyle, this is the first step you need to take. Today. And making it public holds you accountable to achieve it.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I want to help you discover your powerful vision for your lifestyle business. It starts on getting clear about your perfect day.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Let&rsquo;s get started!</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><em>Have you ever taken the time to truly think about your perfect day?</em></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p dir="ltr" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you could wake up tomorrow and do whatever you wanted, be anywhere you desired, and with whoever you choose, what would that day look like?</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Too few people take time to daydream about their perfect day, but the thing is once you write it out clearly, even on just one page, you will actually start to experience more perfect days in your everyday life.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">You&rsquo;ll be amazed at how you can achieve this more easily than you think &ndash; that&rsquo;s how powerful getting clear and writing it down in detail can be for you.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Taking that further you want do the same for not just one day, but your business and life.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <strong>The key way to do this is to create your Painted Picture.</strong> This an amazing tool I take all my coaching and workshop clients through.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> It was originally shared with me by Cameron Herold, Author of Double Double and I created mine in January 2013 on a beach in Malaysia, on a digital sabbatical.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> This is a three year vision and plan, but written in the present tense, as if everything has already come true. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s so powerful, that 60% of what I wrote down and visualized came true by the end of that year!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <a href="http://bit.ly/tsepaintedpic" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Read this post on how to create your own Painted Picture</a> and see mine (which has had over 32,000+ views now on Slideshare) and gone on to inspire many to create their own and start making their dreams come true.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <strong>From there you turn this Painted Picture into your 1 Page Business Plan</strong>, which is your path to profit and continuing success for the next 12 months, including your goals, objectives and revenue streams.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> You can&rsquo;t just have a vision and no accompanying plan of how to break it down into what you need to do today, this week and next month now can you?</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Learn how to create your own 1 Page Biz Plan and<a href="http://bit.ly/1pagebizplan" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"> download my free template right here.</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Now, what I want to know is this; <em>when would now be a good time to create your own Painted Picture and 1 Page Business Plan?</em></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Honestly you can do both of these in just a few hours this weekend &ndash; I promise you can!</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">By the way, I cover this in much more depth in The Freedom Plan Program that I''m launching fully in September after running a sold out pilot program, where I guarantee you will create the blueprint for your own profitable business and lifestyle of freedom.</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> If you&rsquo;d like to be on the VIP early interest list then&nbsp;<a href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12584/3129921422f340f2/2484668/6ac82dc418d16534" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">enter your details here.</a></span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Yours in freedom,</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Natalie Sisson </span> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong>Natalie Sisson</strong></font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Chief Adventurer And Freedom Fighter</font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><a href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com" target="_blank">suitcaseentrepreneur.