ile fulfilling your personal and professional wants and needs.<br /> <br /> Welcome and Enjoy!<br /> <br /> To Your Continued Success,<br /><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/acceleratedlearning/BTSig_Black.gif" alt="Brian Tracy" width="216" height="86" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div style="padding-top:20px;padding-bottom:20px;">\r\n<a href=''http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201174&amp;ebr=182247427''><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/media.briantracy.com/special_offers/sales-cert-1.jpg" style="width:100%;max-width:640px;" border="0"></a>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201175&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201176&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201177&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201178&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201179&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=201180&amp;ebr=182247427" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div> \r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>\r\n<td id="footer" style="color:#222222;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;background-color:#d9d9d9;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:14px;">\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;