(244, 'AUG1489245N', 'AUG1489245N140807072729', 'parent', 'autonews@crainnewsalerts.com', 0, 'NO', 'Automotive News Europe', 'Highlights from top manufacturer and supplier news in Europe', 'crain Communications Inc', '<p>Automotive News Europe is headquartered in Detroit, United States, and celebrates its 17th anniversary in 2013.</p>\n\n<p>Automotive News Europe, a member of the Automotive News Group, was launched in 1996 as the only pan-European biweekly publication for the automotive industry. It was recognized as the leading authority in the industry, covering automakers, their original equipment suppliers, marketing, technology and distribution networks.</p>\n\n<p>In 2010, Automotive News Europe&#39;s format changed to an online-only publication. In 2012, Automotive News Europe launched the Automotive News Europe E-Magazine Edition to complement the already extensive online operation at AutoNewsEurope.com that includes daily and monthly newsletters, breaking news alerts, industry awards, conferences and events.<br />\nThe site is owned by Crain Communications Inc., publisher of more than 27 special interest publications (see links below), including Automotive News &mdash; the pre-eminent newspaper covering the North American automotive industry.</p>\n', 'If you wish to cancel your subscription to this newsletter click here', 'http://crainnewsalerts.com/portal/unsubscribeconfirm/?VjeImOhhpDswltCG8EJq592uFwJ0JRi3A', '1', 'MI 48207', 'Detroit', '', 1, '12,17', '20,21,2,24,22', 'Automotive News', 'NO', '0', 'http://www.europe.autonews.com', '', '81be09219cfc7a4b2e4e0cc7306d6893.jpg', '<p>Automotive News Europe remains the leading business-to-business news outlet in more than 30 countries providing invaluable European sales and production data, in-depth looks at new automotive technologies, show guides to the major auto shows, top level interviews and market analyses.</p>\n\n<p>This e-mail notification is sent the first week of every month, when the newest digital edition of Automotive News Europe becomes available. View our editors&rsquo; collection of Europe&rsquo;s top 20 headlines, and customize the book each month by adding your choice of additional articles. Download the document for easy viewing on your desktop, tablet or mobile device at your convenience.</p>\n', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', '', 'monthly', 0, '2014-08-07 07:27:29', '2014-08-07 07:17:52', 'Active'),
