ink" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div id="main" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:16px;">\r\n<p>Hi aug1436881n,</p>\r\n<p>Do you know what I LOVE most about debt? Getting out of it.</p>\r\n<p>I''ve been there before, in fact, most of us have. I was living out of my car at one point.</p>\r\n<p>The difference is that some people are willing to do whatever it takes to erase their debt, and others remain stagnant; frozen in overwhelm.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134357&amp;ebr=184021488">Learn how to erase your debt here.</a></p>\r\n<p>I want you to take a moment and think about all the things you&rsquo;ve bought on credit recently (other than your home).</p>\r\n<p>From fast cars to sleek technological devices and trendy clothes to faraway vacations, it&rsquo;s common for people today to rack up debt in a frenzy of instant gratification.</p>\r\n<p>The problem there, is that people wind up broke when they finally retire, scraping by on pensions or Social Security.</p>\r\n<p>But what if I told you that right now, you could start taking steps toward achieving financial freedom, that would make you completely independent by the time you wanted to retire?</p>\r\n<p><strong>That&rsquo;s what &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple&rdquo; is about: it&rsquo;s about learning how to create a permanent change in your mindset that allows you to get you out of debt, for good, and to then implement strategies other people have used for centuries to become wealthy.&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134358&amp;ebr=184021488">Order "Wealth Building Made Simple" here</a>.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134359&amp;ebr=184021488"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/wealth/assets/img/program.jpg" alt="" width="193" height="190" /></a></p>\r\n<p>No matter where you&rsquo;re starting out, you CAN implement these time-tested, proven methods.</p>\r\n<p><strong>When you listen to &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple,&rdquo; you learn:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The 5 reasons people DON&rsquo;T become wealthy (you can overcome every single one of these &ndash; which ones are holding you back?)</li>\r\n<li>How to do the research you need to understand WHY and&nbsp; HOW you invest for success (Russian Roulette just won&rsquo;t work, here)</li>\r\n<li>The 7 principles for business success, and how to use them to your advantage</li>\r\n<li>The skill that accounts for 90% of your business success (it&rsquo;s learnable!) &ndash; and why small changes and adjustments in this area can improve your business dramatically</li>\r\n<li>The single biggest reason for failure in adult life &ndash; and how it can paralyze you when it comes to starting your own business</li>\r\n<li>The Great Law of real estate &ndash; knowing this can make your success, and not knowing it can break your success</li>\r\n<li>3 main reasons creativity is so important in becoming financially successful</li>\r\n<li>An action you can take, starting today, to greatly enhance your chances of becoming wealthy</li>\r\n<li>And much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>No matter how much debt you have, or how hopeless your finances may seem, you can turn it around by making small, daily changes that add up over time. All you have to do is begin.</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134360&amp;ebr=184021488">Take the first step now</a>--it''s the most important thing you can do if you''re ready to make a change.</p>\r\n<p>To your financial freedom,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. My last 2 &ldquo;Made Simple&rdquo; offers sold out in record time &ndash; and I''m anticipating this one will, too. <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134361&amp;ebr=184021488">So if you want in, get in now.</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134362&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134363&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134364&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134365&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134366&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=134367&amp;ebr=184021488" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div> \r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>\r\n<td id="footer" style="color:#222222;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;background-color:#d9d9d9;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:14px;">\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Change Your Email</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;"><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/ce.aspx?c=EaUUAKwLAAAC" style="color:#1d3c5a;">Update your email address</a>.</p>\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Get Involved!</p>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom:14px;margin-left:0px;margin-right:0px;margin-top:0px;"><im