ound-color: #ffffff;">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n<img align="left" alt="Company Logo" border="0" height="94" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/schefren-wefcdubimjisvdtdokmotehvjorlvttt-v2" style="margin: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0;\r\nbackground: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;\r\nvertical-align: bottom;" title="Company Logo" width="370" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" cellpadding="20" cellspacing="0" style="width: 600px;\r\nbackground-color: #ffffff;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 20px; border: none;\r\nwhite-space: normal; line-height: normal; background-color: #ffffff;" valign="top">\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Hey\r\nKnewdog,</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">This is why I love Dan\r\nKennedy. He is always telling</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">it like it is and\r\npushing the marketing envelope.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">I just had to share\r\nwith you the email that he sent to</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">HIS list about his new\r\nvideo. It''s one of the best</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">I''ve read in a\r\nwhile.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">It''s classic\r\nDan...powerful, a bit offensive and highly</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">effective.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">You can read it below,\r\nbut don''t just read it study it</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">and when you''re done\r\nbe sure to <a href="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/13117/3097d0165f6c35c2/384909185/34d0310c3c283e70"><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">watch his new video</font></a></font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">too.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">To higher\r\nprofits,</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Rich</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">P.S. There is a ton you\r\ncan learn from Dan''s email and</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">his new video. It''s\r\nfilled with even more moneymaking</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">lessons.\r\n<a href="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/13119/8483a90d5b4730f4/384909185/34d0310c3c283e70"><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Check it out now.</font></a></font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">_________________</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Dan''s Email:\r\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; Subject line: Academic egghead, B.S.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">Dan Kennedy here with a\r\n<a href="https://schefren.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/13121/8380c894c9cb1632/384909185/34d0310c3c283e70"><font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">new video</font></a> for you.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">As I expected, some\r\npeople were offended by my first</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">video where I talked\r\nabout the 7 triggers of mind</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">control.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">I guess this was too\r\n&ldquo;manipulative&rdquo; and offended their</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">sensibilities.\r\nI&rsquo;d also guess these folks couldn&rsquo;t</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">sell their way out of\r\na wet paper bag.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">So much the better for\r\nyou and me.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">In today&rsquo;s video,\r\nI take it a step further by</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">revealing the\r\narchitecture behind sales and marketing</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">messages in print,\r\nvideo, online, offline - whatever,</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">that gets money in the\r\nbank.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">This is NOT\r\n&ldquo;theory&rdquo; spewed out by academic eggheads</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">who never had to sell\r\na product or service in order to</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">eat.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">This IS what works in\r\nthe real world to get people to</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">buy whatever it is\r\nyou&rsquo;re selling and buy now.</font>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">It is what I use and\r\nwhat my customers and clients use</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face="tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif" size="3">to get rich. (Those\r\nwho have the stomachs to actually</font> \r\n<br />\r\n <font face