tom:0px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">\r\n<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<div id="bt1" style="color:#ffffff;padding-top:17px;font-size:16px;">Brian Tracy''s</div>\r\n<div id="bt2" style="color:#ffffff;line-height:100%;margin-top:7px;font-weight:bold;font-size:25px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:0px;">Success Newsletter</div>\r\n<div id="bt3" style="color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:15px;padding-top:7px;font-size:14px;">For Sales and Leadership Achievement</div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding-left:20px;vertical-align:bottom;">\r\n<div id="bt4" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;width:1px;height:1px;display:none;"><img id="btimg" src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/email/brian-tracy.png" alt="" height="1" width="1" style="width:1px;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;" /></div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr></table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="line" style="background-color:#c2c2c2;height:2px;"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><!--[if gte mso 9]>*/</style><![endif]-->\r\n<div id="top-nav" style="overflow:hidden;max-height:1px;height:1px;display:none;">\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150248&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150249&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150250&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150251&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150252&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n    <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150253&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div>\r\n<div id="main" style="background-color:#ffffff;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:16px;">\r\n<p>Hi aug1436881n,</p>\r\n<p>A few days ago, I asked you a very important question:</p>\r\n<p>How would you like to get out of debt?</p>\r\n<p>Even better, how would you like to live with the confidence that you&rsquo;re building a financial fortress; that when you retire, you&rsquo;ll be a millionaire?</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150254&amp;ebr=184973253">Now you can.</a></p>\r\n<p>Thanks to my brand new program, &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple,&rdquo; you have the opportunity to develop the mindset and skills to not only get out of debt, but to also become wealthy.</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150255&amp;ebr=184973253">Get the details here.</a>--<strong>Introductory pricing available for a short time only!</strong></p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150256&amp;ebr=184973253"><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/wealth/assets/img/program.jpg" alt="" width="172" height="173" /></a></p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re like so many of my students, I can guess the thoughts that may be going through your mind right now:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>I don&rsquo;t have ANYTHING. Forget a financial fortress &ndash; I can barely pay my monthly electric bill.</li>\r\n<li>I&rsquo;m not smart enough to make my mortgage, much less millions.</li>\r\n<li>I just have bad luck. I&rsquo;d never be lucky enough to become wealthy.</li>\r\n<li>Something always comes up that keeps me from saving money &ndash; I&rsquo;ll never be able to save.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150257&amp;ebr=184973253">Good news: you&rsquo;re completely wrong.</a></p>\r\n<p>No matter where you are now, you have inside of you the potential and the ability to get out of debt, and to build a healthy financial future for yourself.</p>\r\n<p>And I''ll teach you how, in my <strong>BRAND-NEW</strong> &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple.&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p><strong>When you listen to this 15-CD program, containing more than 8 hours of instruction, you learn:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>The 5 reasons people DON&rsquo;T become wealthy (you can overcome every single one of these &ndash; which ones are holding you back?)</li>\r\n<li>The 3 places you continually see the Law of Correspondence &ndash; your relationships, wealth and the faces of others &ndash; and why, if you&rsquo;re not seeing what you want to, you hold the power to change it</li>\r\n<li>How to do the research you need to understand WHY and&nbsp; HOW you invest for success (Russian Roulette just won&rsquo;t work, here)</li>\r\n<li>The oldest rule for success in America &ndash; follow it and achieve your dreams of financial success</li>\r\n<li>The 7 principles for business success, and how to use them to your advantage</li>\r\n<li>The skill that accounts for 90% of your business success (it&rsquo;s learnable!) &ndash; and why small changes and adjustments in this area can improve your business dramatically</li>\r\n<li>The single biggest reason for failure in adult life &ndash; and how it can paralyze you when it comes to starting your own business</li>\r\n<li>The Great Law of real estate &ndash; knowing this can make your success, and not knowing it can break your success</li>\r\n<li>3 main reasons creativity is so important in becoming financially successful</li>\r\n<li>An action you can take, starting today, to greatly enhance your chances of becoming a millionaire</li>\r\n<li>And much more!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>You hold the power to create your own wealth. And you&rsquo;ll do so faster and easier by following in the footsteps of those who have done it before you.</p>\r\n<p>The lessons in &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple&rdquo; are based not only on my own experience, but also on years of research into what makes success.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150258&amp;ebr=184973253">Order it today!</a></p>\r\n<p>To your financial freedom,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n<p>P.S. I''m offering &ldquo;Wealth Building Made Simple&rdquo; at an incredibly low price &ndash; just like my other "Made Simple" programs, <strong>this WILL sell out</strong>. <a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150259&amp;ebr=184973253">If you&rsquo;re interested, order your copy now.</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="bottom-nav" style="overflow:hidden;padding-bottom:10px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:0px;padding-top:10px;">\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150260&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Home</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150261&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Personal Development</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150262&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Sales Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150263&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Business Training</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150264&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Time Management</a>\r\n<a href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=150265&amp;ebr=184973253" class="nav-link" style="margin-right:6px;color:#1d3c5a;">Leadership</a> \r\n</div> \r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>\r\n<td id="footer" style="color:#222222;font-size:14px;font-family:Verdana,Arial,Sans-Serif;background-color:#d9d9d9;padding-bottom:14px;padding-left:10px;padding-right:10px;padding-top:14px;">\r\n<p class="ftitle" style="margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;margin-bottom:0px;margin-top:0px;font-weight:bold;padding-bottom:4px;padding-left:0px