(295, 'AUG1483403N', 'AUG1483403N140818030257', 'child', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', 0, 'NO', 'Natalie Sisson', 'Step 2: How to target and attract your ideal customer', 'Natalie Sisson', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Natalie Sisson', 'NO', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head><body>\r\n<div id="mainContent" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: rgb(255,255,255); width: 100%; height: 100%;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="preheader" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 10px 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div contentid="preheader" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div>\r\nHaving trouble viewing this email? <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11932/942848512b1d0203/2522542/4603630c3702f07a" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Click here</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="header" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255);">\r\n<div>\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div style="display: block; text-align: center;">\r\n<img align="bottom" alt="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" border="0" height="82" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-e5ba5c06-5717-4bff-a538-3704df735fa9-v2" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; vertical-align: bottom;" title="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" width="600" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="header" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="title" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Are you ready for Step 2 Knewdog?</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I hope so cos it&rsquo;s the one piece of building a business that so many entrepreneurs skip past and it costs them greatly.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">And I&rsquo;ll admit to struggling with this myself for at least the first 12 months of starting my business.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Step 2: Understanding your niche and your ideal customer</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">These two aspects are quite possibly the most critical when it comes to building a successful business.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Yet so few entrepreneurs, even those with established businesses, can actually answer why they do what they do and exactly who they&rsquo;re serving.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Get this part right and you&rsquo;re going to have a wildly successful business, working with people you love and who value you what you do and are customers for life.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><em><strong>Natalie how do I identify my niche and dominate it?</strong></em></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Well I&rsquo;m going to give you a sneak peak into the step-by-step guide I give you to discover your niche in <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12016/cd096266fc6612db/2522542/4603630c3702f07a" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Am I Your Customer</a>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The first trick is to <strong>find a niche that where you can be authentic</strong> and unabashedly you. By that I mean you offer products and services that feel right to you and that you&rsquo;re proud to sell.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">In order to do that you need to choose something that:</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">A. &nbsp;You are passionate about</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">B. That you feel you&rsquo;re in alignment with and;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">C. You want to be spending your time doing.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">This offering should also be a reflection of your talents and skills and values too and combine the whole story of you, your past and why what you do is important.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">You might be wondering how on earth you figure that out, if you haven&rsquo;t already and this where I come to the second step which is <strong>knowing your sweetspot</strong>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">This is the intersection between what you&rsquo;re really good at, what you enjoy doing and what people will pay you for.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I wrote a pretty in-depth post on it that&rsquo;s helped a ton of people in <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11988/1b96d3525e3de4e1/2522542/4603630c3702f07a" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">The Secret to Finding Your Sweet Spot</a>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you already have that figured out then you might be asking&hellip;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><em><strong>How do I know who my ideal customer is Natalie and how do I attract them?</strong></em></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">An excellent question and there&rsquo;s no easy answer to this. It does take time to figure out who you really want to work with.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I call them your red carpet clients. Those people who you love to work with because they respect your knowledge and skills, are all too happy to pay you well, let you know the work without interfering, and rave about you to others.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">These people don&rsquo;t just fall in your lap though. You have a number of things you can do to attract them like a magnet.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I wrote a post about how to attract your red carpet clients <a  href="http://bit.ly/SUg1sb" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">right here</a>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>To select your target market begin by asking yourself these questions:</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Of all the people who could use my product or service, who am I most passionate about working with? Who do I most closely identify with, understand &ndash; even sympathize with&_</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I take you through a powerful exercise to identify your ideal customer in Am I Your Customer and also provide some specific examples that will help you.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Creating an avatar of exactly who this person is has transformed my business. In fact I have three avatars based on knowing and understanding what my community members need.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">This has come from asking them over the years and interviewing people one-on-one to really dig deep into what I can do to solve their problems.&nbsp;In fact you can see the three types of people in the Suitcase Entrepreneur community<a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12018/3665f309e74fe12d/2522542/4603630c3702f07a" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"> right here</a> (and yes I have detailed descriptions and visuals plus names for my avatars in my head, and on my laptop).</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Before you know it you&rsquo;ll be creating products and services your avatars can&rsquo;t wait to get their hands on &ndash; and that&rsquo;s when you know you have a real business.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>That&rsquo;s about the time that you realize you need to answer this question&hellip;</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">How do I work out what I should charge and make sure I&rsquo;m not underpricing myself?</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">When you&rsquo;re just starting out it can be a wise idea to offer up your coaching, web design or translation services, for example, for less than your competition, or what you&rsquo;d like to charge.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The reason for this is you want to get experience working with clients, do amazing work for them and to get them the results they want.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you do that from the get go you&rsquo;ll quickly get great testimonials and referrals for more work. Then you can start to raise your prices to factor in your admin time, follow-up time as well as the time you spend working with your client or on your product.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">While I do cover how to raise your prices and to determine what you should charge in my guide, I also wrote a post here on <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11990/c1a8cffe416c5444/2522542/4603630c3702f07a" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">how to charge what you&rsquo;re worth</a> so check that out.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I hope this email has started the wheels turning on what area you specifically need to work on to get really clear and take your business to the next level.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Stay tuned for Step 3 in a few days time.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">By the way if you&rsquo;re enjoying this series can you do me a favor and click to tweet the following, or copy and paste it on your fave social media site to share this with your friends:&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>Click to tweet:</strong> <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11956/4401a8a4707be552/2129072/fefbc7bf2207294b" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">I&rsquo;m digging this &lsquo;6 Steps to Creating a Profitable Business and a Lifestyle You Adore&rsquo; series. Get it here http://bit.ly/T8z8ib #TSE</a></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Thank you!&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Natalie</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="text" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n<p style="