(296, 'AUG1483403N', 'AUG1483403N140818030503', 'child', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', 0, 'NO', 'Natalie Sisson', 'Step 3: Build your powerful brand', 'Natalie Sisson', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Natalie Sisson', 'NO', 'natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML>\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n</head><body>\r\n<div id="mainContent" style="text-align: left;">\r\n<table cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: rgb(255,255,255); width: 100%; height: 100%;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td valign="top">\r\n<table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 600px;">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="preheader" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 10px 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;">\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div contentid="preheader" style="font-size: 11px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: center;">\r\n<div>\r\nHaving trouble viewing this email? <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/11958/11a3d61dbb1e641f/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">Click here</a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="header" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padding: 0; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; height: 30px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255);">\r\n<div>\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div contentid="image">\r\n<div style="display: block; text-align: center;">\r\n<img align="bottom" alt="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" border="0" height="82" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-e5ba5c06-5717-4bff-a538-3704df735fa9-v2" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; vertical-align: bottom;" title="Welcome to the Suitcase Entrepreneur" width="600" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="header" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="title" style="font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="text" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Why hello again Knewdog</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Today I want to share with you one of my fave topics &ndash; how to build a powerful brand.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> If I&rsquo;m honest my entire business is built on me, Natalie Sisson, the Suitcase Entrepreneur, as the brand. Everything I stand for and do &ndash; freedom, integrity, fun, adventure and savvy business building, only serves to strengthen my brand.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> I&rsquo;ve learned to monetize myself. I give away 90% of my knowledge for free through my blog, podcast, videos, interviews and manifesto.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">The 10% I charge for is business design coaching, digital products and services, my exclusive BYOB program and my Highflyer membership club, workshops, retreats, my bestselling book and speaking.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Now not all of this happened at once. I took it one step at a time and started off with running social media workshops and then coaching my first clients to bring in immediate revenue, and prove to myself that I had what it takes to really help people achieve their ultimate lifestyle business.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> That&rsquo;s my unique path. What about yours? Let&rsquo;s take a look.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <strong>Step 3: Build your powerful brand</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Standing out from the crowd is hugely important and you do that by building your personal brand and credibility through focusing on what you do best &ndash; your unique strengths and skills that only you can offer.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">If you are still struggling with what this is, don&rsquo;t forget to revisit my video and post on &lsquo;<a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12014/7291969e2efd16ca/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">How to find your sweetspot</a>&rsquo;.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Once you back your unique offering up with a strategic content marketing plan and a solid social media strategy you&rsquo;ll be able to attract your ideal customers and become the go-to person in your niche, like never before.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>So how do you do that exactly? In three ways.</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <strong>#1 Build a website that sells and that you&rsquo;re proud of </strong> </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Want to build a profitable business but don&rsquo;t have ANY online presence? Shame on you. How on earth do you expect people to find you? &nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">While I get that face to face networking and interaction is important, it has to go hand-in-hand with online marketing and promotion. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> And nowadays it&rsquo;s easier than ever to put up a website thanks to WordPress and their lovely themes. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Here&rsquo;s a fun and valuable blog post on how to set your website up in four simple steps <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12008/cc0166510e5a0c7f/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">How To Plan, Build, And Launch Your Own Website In 4 Days</a>.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">There''s no need to spend a ton of money upfront. Invest a few hundred dollars and you&rsquo;re off and running. As your business grows you can invest a lot more in quality design and customization - which I do highly recommend. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Really stumped on where to start, or blaming your perfectionist tendencies for your lack of website? Might I suggest trying <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12026/7115a3d9206a723c/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">LeadPages</a>.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">In my humble opinion this is the perfect choice for the entrepreneur who wants the simplest way to create a simple yet elegant landing page that requires no knowledge of coding or anything technical, or the need for hosting.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">That way you can pick one of their templates, put in your text, photo and whatever elements you want in a few clicks, and before you know it you have a webpage that explains who you are, what you do and why that matters.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Plus on that page you can sell your goods, or at least offer an incentive to get them to subscribe to your list with their email, so that you can then start building trust and a closer relationship with them before you sell to them.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I cover Crafting a website that attracts, converts and sells like crazy in<a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12012/6b51b8122eb0ff7c/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"> my highly popular BYOB Build Your Online Business guide</a>. Hundreds of customers have followed my advice in here to get &lsquo;unstuck&rsquo; and launch a website they&rsquo;re proud of and that actually helps them make money.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>#2. Start a blog that matters and positions you as the leader in your market&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Here&rsquo;s a widely known fact by my freedom fighting community. My business started from a blog. Yep just a simple blog. It wasn&rsquo;t fancy. The design was simple and minimalist. And I just adored writing and sharing my knowledge.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Now monetizing a blog is a whole other ball game entirely, and to be straight up, I wouldn&rsquo;t recommend it as a path to profitability as it&rsquo;s REALLY hard to make money from a blog.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">But a blog is a brilliant tool to build your brand and therefore business and therefore make money. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">How that works is a blog acts as your own press agency, a way to promote yourself in a non douchebag way. You get to share your knowledge, show your expertise, write great content that actually helps people. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">You get to show case studies from results you got for your clients or customers that go way further than you trying to sell your stuff. If I&rsquo;m going to buy a product or service from you, show me the results you&rsquo;ve gotten others and I&rsquo;m IN! </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> Blogs let you show your personality. Weather you&rsquo;re funny, insightful, brash, bold, shy, quirky, controversial &ndash; you&rsquo;re uniquely you and if you let that shine through your blog &ndash; whether written, video or audio, you&rsquo;ll attract and grow a pretty awesome community which leads to customers and sales.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12020/73d65db28e02dd83/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">I''d love for you to listen to this episode</a> with Jaime Tardy on the Suitcase Entrepreneur Podcast on how to build a blog that matters. We share a lot of great tips. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><strong>#3. Use social media to build influence and generate leads and new clients&nbsp;</strong></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Social media is an undeniably powerful tool for entrepreneurs, businesses and brands. I''m such a huge advocate of social media as it''s allowed me to build and grow my entire online business and cement my personal brand into the hearts and minds of all those who interact with me online and off.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Without it I would never have achieved the reach and influence and brand visibility for myself and the Suitcase Entrepreneur or achieved a <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12022/c79b28411fd774e7/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">No #1 Bestselling book!</a> &nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">As well as that I''d not have created such amazing friendships with mere strangers on my travels across the world or this amazing community and network of peers, mentors and other freedom fighters. &nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">It''s going to be hugely important for you too. I like to call social media your sales, marketing and customer service team rolled into one and there are plenty of ways you can use it to build your credibility, your visibility, drive more traffic and qualified leads and make sales. I cover this in my book but also in my free <a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12024/69ba9863d10d9d00/2564419/f8218f4bcb47fec1" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">10 Day Social Media Challenge</a>.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Anyway that''s a lot to take in for this email so I''ll leave you to digest on all of this and you''ll see me in a few days to share Step 4.&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Natalie x&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; color: null;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong>Natalie Sisson</strong></font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Chief Adventurer And Freedom Fighter</font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com" target="_blank">suitcaseentrepreneur.com</a><br /> natalie@suitcaseentrepreneur.com&nbsp;<br /> </font></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\n<div contentid="paragraph" style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\n<div>\r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<a style="color:#3B465F;text-decoration:underline;" target="_blank" href="http://knewdog.com"><b style="color:#e46c0a;">To manage your subscriptions, visit your profile at www.knewdog.com.</b></a>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; color: rgb(0,0,0);">\r\nNatalie Sisson<br>NE 7th Ave<br>Portland, Oregon 97211<br>United States\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" cellpadding="20" cellspacing="0" style="width: 600px; background-color: rgb(255,255,255);">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td sectionid="body" style="text-align: left; margin: 0; padd