(300, 'AUG1436881N', 'AUG1436881N140818105103', 'child', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', 0, 'NO', 'Brian Tracy', 'A "plug and play" template that will make them BUY now!', 'Brian Tracy', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, '', '', 'Brian Tracy', 'NO', 'newsletter@briantracyintl.com', '', '', '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN">\r\n<html>\r\n	<head>\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en-us">\r\n	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n	<title>A Message From Brian Tracy</title>\r\n	</head>\r\n	<body><div style=''height:2px;''><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/images/btis186578483.gif" width="10" height="2" alt=""></div>\r\n		<style type="text/css">\r\n	p {margin-bottom: 1em;}\r\n\r\n			.NLTitle {font-weight: normal; font-size: 16pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial;}\r\n			.NLSubtitle {font-weight: bold; font-size: 12pt; color: #336699; font-family: Arial; text-decoration: none;}\r\n			.NLAuthor {font-weight: normal; font-size: 12pt; color: #222222; font-family: Arial; font-style: italic;}\r\n		</style>\r\n		\r\n		<span style="color: #222222; font-weight:normal; font-size:12pt; font-family: Arial;">\r\n\r\n		<p>aug1436881n,</p>\r\n<p><strong>Do you HATE sales techniques or "closing" a sale?</strong></p>\r\n<p>If you do, then you should really<a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209808&ebr=186578483"> try this formula...</a></p>\r\n<p>You see, ideas are a dime a dozen. What YOU need are tools and reliable proven formulas. Dan Kennedy just put his proven formula online.</p>\r\n<p>It''s basically a plug and play template for creating sales and marketing messages that get people to<em><strong> whip out their wallets and buy now.</strong></em></p>\r\n<p><strong>It is, by far, the easiest way to make sales to your customers, clients or patients--and ALOT of ''em.&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209809&ebr=186578483">Get Dan Kennedy''s plug and play template here</a>--and start making sales faster and easier than EVER before!</p>\r\n<p>Whether you''re selling one to one, one to many, online or offline, this formula will make you more money, quicker and with less effort!</p>\r\n<p>Get the proven formula for closing sales the easy way here.</p>\r\n<p>By the way, Dan is not selling anything in this video.</p>\r\n<p>It is 100% pure content that delivers the tools you need in your marketing and sales arsenal.</p>\r\n<p><a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209810&ebr=186578483">Get it here now-</a>-he''s pulling it down soon.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>To your success,</p>\r\n<p><img src="http://www.briantracy.com/files/pages/images/btsig.gif" alt="" /><br /><br />Brian Tracy</p>\r\n\r\n		</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="color:#222222; font-weight:normal;font-size: 10pt; font-family: Arial;"><strong>Get Involved!</strong><br />\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/twitter.gif" alt="twitter" title="Twitter" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nFollow me on \r\n<a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209811&ebr=186578483" style="color:#1d3c5a">Twitter</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/facebook.gif" alt="Facebook" title="Facebook" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nBecome a fan on\r\n<a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209812&ebr=186578483" style="color:#1d3c5a">Facebook</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/linkedin.gif" alt="LinkedIn" title="LinkedIn" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nConnect with me on \r\n<a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209813&ebr=186578483" style="color:#1d3c5a">LinkedIn</a>.<br>\r\n<img src="http://www.briantracy.com/assets2/v7/images/connect/youtube.gif" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" height="15" width="15">&nbsp; \r\nWatch me on <a  href="http://www.briantracy.com/r.aspx?sbe=209814&ebr=186578483" style="color:#1d3c5a">Youtube</a>.<br />\r\n<img src="h