r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="header" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-family: arial; color: rgb(26,36,46); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="title" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 11px; font-weight: normal; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div contentid="text" style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal; overflow: visible; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-align: left;">\r\n<div style="overflow: visible;">\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt;">Howdy Knewdog</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I&rsquo;m visiting Dallas, Texas for the first time! By the time you read this I&rsquo;ll be in the full swing of my final BYOB Build Your Online Business Workshop.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n I can&rsquo;t believe it&rsquo;s the last one of my World Tour after holding them in Melbourne, Auckland, Tokyo, Kyoto and Vancouver. I&rsquo;ve had a lot of people ask if I&rsquo;d hold them in other places but nope, this is it. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n I don&rsquo;t plan on running them next year either as I&rsquo;ve taken everything I teach in this workshop, my bestselling book and my mega successful 30 Day blog challenge,<b style="color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px;"><span style=""></span></b> and rolled it into my proudest creation yet - <a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/freedomplan" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">The Freedom Plan</a>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n In fact I&rsquo;ve made a lot of decisions over the last few weeks while spending time in Whistler and Bowen Island and reconnecting with a lot of dear friends in Vancouver and looking ahead to what my future holds, and how I want to live my life with even more freedom. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<strong>NEWSFLASH:</strong> This has led me to making the decision, after close to 3 years of working with amazing clients around the world, to no longer offer 1-on-1 coaching. Yep that&rsquo;s right. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Although I got so much out of it and delivered some epic results for my clients, I&rsquo;ve realized it&rsquo;s not allowing me to live and travel as freely as I&rsquo;d like by committing to weekly sessions.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px;">I&rsquo;m giving out way too much energy<span style="">&nbsp;</span></span>to my clients and community&nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(0,0,0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px;">that&rsquo;s not sustainable,<span style="">&nbsp;</span></span>and I need to give some back to me by reclaiming that time.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Nor does it allow me to make a real and scaleable impact on my community and my mission to ensure 100,000 + entrepreneurs create freedom in business and adventure in life by 2020.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<strong>So the only way you&rsquo;ll be able to work with me anymore</strong> is if you join my group coaching through the Highflyer Club if you&rsquo;re an established entrepreneur wanting masterminding, mentoring and real applicable missions (<a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/highflyerclub/apply" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">get on the VIP list here</a> to learn when applications open up later this month) </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n OR through my upcoming and brand NEW flagship program that I&rsquo;m SUPER proud of and excited about, The Freedom Plan.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n I believe I&rsquo;ve built (and am currently piloting with fantastic feedback) the world&rsquo;s first online program designed to ensure you DO build a profitable business you can run from anywhere while creating a lifestyle of freedom you deserve -&gt; <a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/freedomplan" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">get on the earlybird list here</a>.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n It&rsquo;s no surprise that I feel connected to those who also live and breathe this philosophy of true freedom, which is why I brought in the one and only Nisha Moodley to be a guest on my podcast this week.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Nisha is a women''s empowerment trainer who believes in empowering the Western woman to build a business and life they love. She goes on to share tips on how to break unproductive routines, what she&rsquo;s learned about outsourcing and team management, as well as her philosophy on freedom based business, so be sure to <a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/104" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">listen to the podcast now</a>!</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Now, if you are inspired to start an online business of your own, but aren&rsquo;t quite sure where to start then you will definitely want to check out <a  href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cMky41C5XeA" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">this week&rsquo;s video</a> where I share 3 more juicy tips on how to do this.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n<a  href="https://kk125.infusionsoft.com/app/linkClick/12991/9685d8b1fa33d083/2528725/92139b16c944954e" nottracked="false" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);"><img align="bottom" alt="3 Juicy Tips for Starting an Online Product-Based Business" border="0" height="385" src="https://d1yoaun8syyxxt.cloudfront.net/kk125-a1258860-5fb6-48c7-b4d9-22a76963eb1f-v2" style="margin: 0; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0; background: none; border: none; white-space: normal; line-height: normal;" title="3 Juicy Tips for Starting an Online Product-Based Business" width="524" /></a> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">I share everything from how to grab leads, why you need to learn how to sell and why a sales funnel is crucial for success.</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n This is the follow on <a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com/lifestyle-business-videos/starting-an-online-business" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">video from last week</a> where I give you 4 key ways to get started with your business. Apparently it&rsquo;s &lsquo;tremendous&rsquo; and has over 100 likes on Facebook!</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n PS I&rsquo;ll be heading up the Women in Podcasting Panel at the first ever Podcast Movement in Dallas this weekend so if you&rsquo;re around <a  href="http://bit.ly/1nZGKB7" shape="rect" style="color: rgb(6,69,173);">grab your tickets here</a> as I&rsquo;d love to meet you. </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"> \r\n<br clear="none" />\r\n Natalie xx&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0; color: null; font-size: 12px; font-family: arial;">\r\n<span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong>Natalie Sisson</strong></font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><strong></strong>Chief Adventurer And Freedom Fighter</font></p><p><font face="verdana,geneva" size="3" style="font-size: small;"><a  href="http://suitcaseentrepreneur.com" target="_blank">suitcaseentrepreneur.com</a><br /> natalie@